description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Yulenka purrs with a rating of 64, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 192, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Stringalong for East, 1 for South, and Stringalong for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80643-77174-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [192 Votes, Top 5% Score]
